OL,4,CJeopardy! host Mike Richards quits
OL,5,Cafter sexist comments surface
OL,6, TV presenter Mike Richards has stepped
OL,7, down as the new co-host of the US quiz
OL,8, show Jeopardy! after sexist comments
OL,9, that he made on a podcast resurfaced.
OL,11,FHis exit comes just nine days after his
OL,12,Fnew role was announced.
OL,14,FPressure grew after a report by The
OL,15,FRinger dug up disparaging comments he
OL,16,Fmade on his podcast The Randumb Show in
OL,17,F2013 and 2014.
OL,19,FMr Richards, who is also the executive
OL,20,Fproducer of the show, said he would be
OL,21,Fstepping down "effective immediately".
